WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:01.573
Well, good evening, family.

00:00:01.573 --> 00:00:03.611
Thank you for joining me again tonight.

00:00:03.611 --> 00:00:04.520
I really appreciate it.

00:00:04.520 --> 00:00:06.809
I have some things I have to say really quick.

00:00:06.809 --> 00:00:09.920
We see these things that we talked about last night.

00:00:09.920 --> 00:00:13.040
Now, last night was very different.

00:00:13.040 --> 00:00:21.342
Everything the Lord showed us in prayer last night was pretty much over the top.

00:00:21.697 --> 00:00:29.849
I believe I saw Ezekiel, and he was standing on the side of a mountain, and I saw a valley of desolate dryness.

00:00:33.680 --> 00:00:37.707
It was black and white; it wasn't in color.

00:00:37.707 --> 00:00:42.227
It looked like spiritual warfare.

00:00:43.480 --> 00:00:55.967
And as the valley was black and white, as I was looking into the vision, I could see Ezekiel standing up with a long robe with holes in his gown.

00:00:57.375 --> 00:01:03.950
It had holes all in it at the bottom where it would drag the rocks, because they didn't have pavement back then.

00:01:04.460 --> 00:01:19.279
But he had a long shofar in his hands that was a massive horn, and his beard was clear down to the middle of his belly in the vision, and it was gray.

00:01:19.279 --> 00:01:28.920
His hair was long; his facial hair was very thick and long, like he had been in the wilderness.

00:01:37.720 --> 00:01:46.739
As he was standing there, I saw light beside him and I could see all these clouds.

00:01:46.739 --> 00:01:58.719
I heard from a distance with a thunderous voice, "Can these bones live?

00:01:58.719 --> 00:02:03.538
" And all of a sudden, he took that shofar and he blew it.

00:02:03.973 --> 00:02:17.280
It was a long blast, and it was very beautiful sounding, but it echoed the presence of God through that valley.

00:02:17.650 --> 00:02:28.239
The glory of the Lord went through that valley, and water started to come from a massive tree.

00:02:28.666 --> 00:02:36.239
It didn't come from the tree; it went by the tree, because there are scriptures that back this.

00:02:36.575 --> 00:02:48.839
I saw the river of this water start to flow the moment he blew the horn, and it started going over this cliff of a beautiful rock.

00:03:00.702 --> 00:03:02.756
He was standing, then he sat down and took his place of authority by resting at the edge of this rock, and the water came over and he was looking at it.

00:03:02.756 --> 00:03:13.520
I saw the tree, and it was one of those large sequoia trees, a massive tree that was right by the river of water.

00:03:13.520 --> 00:03:21.291
As I was looking into this, I saw a piece of fruit that was cut in half.

00:03:21.291 --> 00:03:27.679
There was a seed in the fruit that looked like a peach pit, covered with blood.

00:03:35.360 --> 00:03:35.840
It was covered with the blood of Jesus.

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:46.276
And the Lord was showing us that all the seeds laid dormant, but they're not dead.

00:03:48.204 --> 00:03:50.640
The seeds from the past will have a harvest come at last.

00:03:50.640 --> 00:04:01.029
I saw the manifestation of all the seeds we've sowed, whether they be bad or good; seed time and harvest never ceases.

00:04:04.033 --> 00:04:05.176
The Lord gave us Genesis 8.

00:04:16.512 --> 00:04:17.024
I saw seed time and harvest accelerating, and I saw the blessing.

00:04:17.536 --> 00:04:25.720
The Lord said, "Pray over your past seeds for a crop failure.

00:04:47.440 --> 00:04:54.720
" So we call for a crop failure over our past seeds so that they don't bear any fruit.

00:04:58.274 --> 00:05:05.919
It was absolutely beautiful what I was seeing, and he gave the scriptures.

00:05:05.919 --> 00:05:14.776
Then I saw a baby in a bassinet stroller that was braided with gold.

00:05:15.851 --> 00:05:26.548
It was a white bassinet, and the baby was laying in it with one of those gowns that you use when you take them to get dedicated before the Lord.

00:05:29.100 --> 00:05:36.740
It was a beautiful white gown that was sparkling with glitter and glowing, and I could see the presence of the Lord on that baby.

00:05:37.120 --> 00:05:44.773
The feet of the baby were kicking around, excited, like it's cooing and excited about life.

00:05:52.507 --> 00:05:57.039
I couldn't see the baby, but I could see the feet.

00:05:57.039 --> 00:06:06.951
Then I saw a man with no face; it looked like a face with a veil over it.

00:06:06.951 --> 00:06:12.903
I couldn't make it out, but he had the same gown on as the baby did.

00:06:13.375 --> 00:06:17.706
He was looking over in that baby's bassinet.

00:06:19.819 --> 00:06:28.240
You couldn't see what he was focused on because there were no eyes, nose, or mouth, but I could see his face was toward the baby.

00:06:28.740 --> 00:06:35.719
The Lord started talking to us about coming as a child, that we're God's children.

00:06:48.639 --> 00:06:48.895
Then I saw a fox with a black charcoal nose and eyes.

00:06:57.474 --> 00:06:59.484
It was a big fox.

00:07:04.960 --> 00:07:20.070
The small foxes spoil the vines, but as I could see the cliff where the water was coming down, I saw this fox looking up at the water and looking at Ezekiel.

00:07:20.420 --> 00:07:28.110
It was staring with a gaze, but it didn't do anything.

00:07:30.639 --> 00:07:40.160
But as I saw this, I saw a pair of lungs inside of that waterfall.

00:07:41.100 --> 00:07:46.320
The lungs were detached from the body, and they were breathing.

00:07:53.303 --> 00:07:53.669
The water was filling them up; it was Holy Spirit.

00:07:56.320 --> 00:07:56.560
You could see the lungs exhale and inhale.

00:07:57.510 --> 00:08:01.599
It was the living water that was flowing out of those lungs.

00:08:09.920 --> 00:08:10.240
I could see the veins; I could see the trachea.

00:08:19.405 --> 00:08:21.737
It was highlighted in a beautiful blue.

00:08:28.427 --> 00:08:28.764
As I see these visions, the Lord was showing me that scripture from Ezekiel 47.

00:08:28.764 --> 00:08:34.400
Fruit trees of all kinds will grow on both banks of the river.

00:08:34.400 --> 00:08:39.546
Their leaves will not wither, nor will their fruit fail.

00:08:39.546 --> 00:08:43.739
Every month they will bear fruit because the water from the sanctuary flows to them.

00:08:53.360 --> 00:08:53.931
Their fruit will serve for food and their leaves for healing.

00:08:59.999 --> 00:09:03.577
I thought it was cool because people found that, and it validates the vision more.

00:09:15.839 --> 00:09:16.053
You don't want to be flaky.

00:09:16.053 --> 00:09:21.088
He's trying to get a hold of his body because there's a great shaking.

00:09:21.088 --> 00:09:37.630
I saw these major events taking place on New Year's Eve, and we are praying for our nation next Wednesday night: New York, Las Vegas, New Orleans, Miami, Nevada, Beverly Hills—every one of these places that would try to have a terrorist attack.

00:09:42.015 --> 00:09:43.990
