00:09:43.990 --> 00:09:53.484
We pray for a supernatural protection over our people that every single plot, every single plan would be uncovered by the blood of Jesus.

00:10:04.229 --> 00:10:04.571
I believe that we have authority over serpents and scorpions and nothing shall by any means hurt us.

00:10:07.760 --> 00:10:13.680
